@startuml SPI_Arb_FSM

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor LightGreen
    BorderColor DarkGreen
    FontSize 12
}

title SPI Arbiter (spi_arb) – Round-Robin State Machine

[*] --> IDLE : rst

state IDLE : busy = 0\nMonitor a_req, b_req\n(live go | pending)

state GRANT : ctrl_go = 1\nLatch winner's data\ngrant_hold = grant_pick\nrr_pref flips

state BUSY_XFER : busy = 1\nRoute busy/done to granted client\nLatch incoming requests\nfrom other client as pending

state COMPLETE : ctrl_done received\nbusy = 0\nRoute done + rx_data\nto granted client

note right of IDLE
  <b>Arbitration (combinational):</b>
  grant_pick =
    both request → rr_pref (round-robin)
    only A       → 0 (A wins)
    only B       → 1 (B wins)
end note

note right of BUSY_XFER
  <b>Pending latch:</b>
  If the losing client pulses go
  during a transfer, the request
  is stored as pending and will
  be served next.
end note

IDLE --> GRANT : a_req | b_req

GRANT --> BUSY_XFER : [latch held_wlen, held_rlen,\nheld_tx_data, held_cs_sel]

BUSY_XFER --> COMPLETE : ctrl_done\n(from spi_ctrl)

COMPLETE --> GRANT : a_req | b_req\n[pending request ready]
COMPLETE --> IDLE : !a_req & !b_req

@enduml
